OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto Sunday with some late evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry overnight and
OL,8,Fskies remaining largely clear across
OL,9,Fthe country. Rather warm and feeling
OL,10,Fmuggy in urban areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FHot and humid on bank holiday
OL,13,FMonday, exceptionally so for late May,
OL,14,Fwith widespread strong sunshine and
OL,15,Flight winds. Slightly fresher at the
OL,16,Fcoast with a sea breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
