OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying sunny and mostly dry over the
OL,7,Fnext few days. Gradually turning less
OL,8,Fhot from Wednesday, though still warm.
OL,9,FA little more patchy cloud developing,
OL,10,Fperhaps with the odd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
